					tr
						td High Power Infrafred LED
						td HIR11-21C/L11/TR8
						td: a(href="/datasheets/HIR11-21C_L11_TR8.pdf") PDF
						

		section.gallery.fourth
			ul
				li: img(src="img/magic_icons/space_invader.jpg") 
				li: img(src="img/magic_icons/mario.jpg") 
				li: img(src="img/magic_icons/nyan_cat.jpg")

		section#contact
			h2 Questions? Just contact us!
			p 
				| If you have questions or suggestions just contact us per 
				a(href="mailto:wizards23+magicshifter@gmail.com") email.

			p 
				| Found anything wrong about this homepage? 
				a(href="https://github.com/magicshifter/magicshifter.net") file an issue on github.

